      "span_text": "The method mentioned in [CITATION_1] could work on an API calls based malware classifier (and provide a better performance for the adversarial sequence generation) only if a single API equivalence attack exists, i.e. if one could find an alternative API that could replace an existing one, preserving its functionality."
    }
